# Express.js Product Management App

This is a simple Express.js web application for managing products. It allows you to view a list of products, see details for each product, update product information, and delete products.

## Features

- View a list of all products on the main page.
- Click on individual product links to view detailed information.
- Update product details using the provided forms.
- Delete products through the application.

## Setup

Clone the repository:

   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/express-product-app.git
------------
Dependencies
Express.js
EJS (Embedded JavaScript templating)
Body-parser
------------
File Structure
/data: Contains static data for products.
/routes: Defines the application routes.
/styles: CSS styles for the application.
/views: EJS templates for rendering HTML.
main.js: The main server file.
-------------
Usage
Navigate to http://localhost:3000 to view the main page.
Click on individual product links to view detailed information.
Use the provided forms to update or delete products.
